adjectives.description: prosopopoeial (comparative more prosopopoeial, superlative most prosopopoeial)

examples: They glut your eares with their Prognostications, and surprising me heretofore, when by my sicknesse I was brought very low and weake, they have injuriously handled me with their Doctrines, positions, prescriptions, magistrall fopperies, and prosopopeyall gravity […].
